{"tid":2112800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"侵侵點名，微信、抖音要顫抖了！","createTime":"2020-07-17T15:00:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T07:31:55.000Z","uid":294518,"like":228,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"23608e46496e69878e3b4d672e6c120f59acdc4a","tid":2112800,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T15:00:19.000Z","msg":"Donald Trump says considering TikTok ban as China row deepens.<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.economictimes.com/news/international/business/donald-trump-says-considering-tiktok-ban-as-china-row-deepens/articleshow/76853635.cms\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.economictimes.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2Fbusiness%2Fdonald-trump-says-considering-tiktok-ban-as-china-row-deepens%2Farticleshow%2F76853635.cms&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpWrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=5c06ea79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.economictimes.com/news/international/business/donald-trump-says-considering-tiktok-ban-as-china-row-deepens/articleshow/76853635.cms</a><br />\n川普說他正在考慮禁止使用抖音，作為懲罰讓冠狀病毒大流行的中共國。他的發言與之前蓬佩奧的說法一致。這家被中國公司所擁有的公司被指充當了北京的間諜工具，雖然其否認。但川普說「我們正在調查」。<br />\n<br />\nNavarro: Expect More Trump Administration Action on TikTok, WeChat<br />\n白宮高級顧問彼得&middot;納瓦羅7月12日表示，他預計川普總統將對抖音和微信採取「強有力的行動」！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theepochtimes.com/navarro-expect-trump-administration-to-take-more-action-on-tiktok-wechat_3422360.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theepochtimes.com%2Fnavarro-expect-trump-administration-to-take-more-action-on-tiktok-wechat_3422360.html&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpWrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=abd81c71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.theepochtimes.com/navarro-expect-trump-administration-to-take-more-action-on-tiktok-wechat_3422360.html</a><br />\n<br />\n美國什麼時候會對抖音和微信採取行動？<br />\n白宮辦公廳主任馬克&middot;梅多斯（Mark Meadows）告訴記者：雖然沒有一個預定的行動期限，但他們考慮的是「幾周」而不是「幾個月」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-trump-tiktok-idUSKCN24G36W\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-usa-trump-tiktok-idUSKCN24G36W&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpWrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=5f06dd66\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-usa-trump-tiktok-idUSKCN24G36W&h=866dd269\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-trump-tiktok-idUSKCN24G36W</a>"},{"pid":"8438842443f82b4847a340bb12ffa0ca61dc6006","tid":2112800,"uid":362827,"like":17,"dislike":6,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T15:02:25.000Z","msg":"哂氣<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538226-20200717.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538226-20200717.htm&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpWrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=d42d3c9c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538226-20200717.htm&h=d33e2eb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538226-20200717.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9a7dd11f7bad96d343013ebd8728eb4d09be5b3b","tid":2112800,"uid":21545,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T15:42:06.000Z","msg":"唔怪之得朱仔會歸美國邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8844b6962043d696fd9a047922e219a39a2b9a0e","tid":2112800,"uid":38482,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T15:43:27.000Z","msg":"in 侵侵 we trust<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a35de3360badd40697379bf2748089dbbfb53d5","tid":2112800,"uid":261913,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"quote":{"pid":"9a7dd11f7bad96d343013ebd8728eb4d09be5b3b","tid":2112800,"uid":21545,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T15:42:06.000Z","msg":"唔怪之得朱仔會歸美國邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkg